title: No survivors in Russian plane crash- reports
text:
No survivors in Russian plane crash- reports 11:05pm IST - 00:37 
A plane has crashed near Moscow, with Russian news agencies reporting all 71 people on board have been killed. Jacob Greaves reports. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
